 to the strong stock market rally after the re-election of President-elect Trump, but also thanks to the stronger dollar, also</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1856702253/image_1856702253.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741977-bond-international-returns-ytd-not-much-to-crow-about", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 13:20:00"}, {"id": "4741995", "title": "Medical Properties Trust Q3: Time To Consider Options", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Call and put option trading signs\" data-id=\"517998631\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3000px\" height=\"2000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">remco86</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>MPW stock: Previous thesis and Q3 earnings</h2> <p>My last coverage on <strong>Medical Properties Trust</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MPW\" title=\"Medical Properties Trust, Inc.\">MPW</a></span>) was published more than a month ago by Seeking Alpha. Under a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730485-medical-properties-trust-q3-preview-rare-insider-buy-indicates-improving-sentiment\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4730485-medical-properties-trust-q3-preview-rare-insider-buy-indicates-improving-sentiment\" target=\"_blank\">title</a> of \"Medical Properties Trust Q3 Preview: Rare Insider Buy Indicates</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/517998631/image_517998631.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741995-medical-properties-trust-q3-time-to-consider-options", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 13:12:23"}, {"id": "4741993", "title": "MPLX: 8% Yield And Strong Dividend Growth", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand holding American currency\" data-id=\"145671149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1176px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>MPLX LP (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MPLX\" title=\"MPLX LP Common Units\">MPLX</a></span>) is a midstream company that has performed very well in 2024 so far. But despite hefty gains, the company offers a high distribution yield of close to 8% and should continue to grow its payout aggressively. Add an</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741993-mplx-stock-8-percent-yield-strong-dividend-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 13:07:54"}, {"id": "4741991", "title": "Nomad Foods Had A Good Q3 2024, But I'm Less Attracted To Its Prospects", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mujer comprar peces en el supermercado congelado\" data-id=\"505524402\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">97/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Nomad Foods (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NOMD\" title=\"Nomad Foods Limited\">NOMD</a></span>) released 3Q24 results with mixed results. Revenues were flat YoY, with the company blaming an ERP installation, without which sales would have been up 3%. Growth returned to some important countries like Germany, and the company is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/505524402/image_505524402.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741991-nomad-foods-had-a-good-3q24-but-im-less-attracted-to-the-companys-prospects", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:56:21"}, {"id": "4741990", "title": "BRW: Strong Recent Performance Has Improved This Fund", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand holding American currency\" data-id=\"145671149\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1176px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Anthony Bradshaw</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The <strong>Saba Capital Income &amp; Opportunities Fund</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRW\" title=\"Saba Capital Income &amp; Opportunities Fund\">BRW</a></span>) is a closed-end fund that offers its investors a very interesting way to obtain income. I describe the fund's strategy as interesting because it invests in a variety of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/145671149/image_145671149.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741990-brw-strong-recent-performance-has-improved-this-fund", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:53:26"}, {"id": "4741989", "title": "CD Projekt: Reclaiming Its Reputation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Anime futuristic people\" data-id=\"1458253752\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1092px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">nemke/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There have been few stories in the video game industry that have captured the attention of the public like the rise, fall, and slow resurgence of CD Projekt (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OTGLY\" title=\"CD Projekt S.A.\">OTCPK:OTGLY</a>). The company was long regarded as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1458253752/image_1458253752.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741989-cd-projekt-reclaiming-its-reputation", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:47:28"}, {"id": "4741988", "title": "VWO: Emerging Markets Face A Slew Of Risks In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man with arms outstretched on cracked background\" data-id=\"1253986380\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8660px\" height=\"5773px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Main Thesis and Background</h2> <p>The purpose of this article is to evaluate the Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VWO\" title=\"Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets Index Fund ETF Shares\">VWO</a></span>) as an investment option. The fund is managed by Vanguard and its <a href=\"https://investor.vanguard.com/etf/profile/VWO\" rel=\"nofollow\">objective</a> is to \"invest in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741988-vwo-emerging-markets-face-a-slew-of-risks-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:43:48"}, {"id": "4741985", "title": "Hafnia Limited: $100 Million Reason To Hold Your Nose And Stick With The Clean Product Trade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock buyback and Share buybacks is shown using the text\" data-id=\"1912124068\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>In September, I wrote two very bullish pieces on the clean product trade for both TORM plc (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TRMD\" title=\"TORM plc\">TRMD</a>) and Hafnia Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HAFN\" title=\"Hafnia Limited\">HAFN</a></span>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723741-hafnia-limited-a-20-percent-yield-and-the-best-value-on-the-water\">The gist of those articles centered around the continued polarization</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741985-hafnia-limited-100-million-reason-to-hold-your-nose-and-stick-with-the-clean-product-trade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:33:22"}, {"id": "4741980", "title": "Vertical Aerospace: Rally Is A Good Selling Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual eVTOL (electric vertical take-off and landing) aircrafts as a taxi/shuttle service at the helipad on top of a building\" data-id=\"1394967815\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 